# Kinetic Gym App — Environment Variables

## Required for local development

```bash
VITE_CONVEX_URL=https://<your-deployment>.convex.cloud
VITE_CONVEX_SITE_URL=https://<your-deployment>.convex.site
CONVEX_DEPLOYMENT=dev:<your-deployment-name>
```

## Required for Vercel deployment

Add these in your Vercel project Settings → Environment Variables:

| Variable | Value | Environment |
|----------|-------|-------------|
| `VITE_CONVEX_URL` | `https://<deployment>.convex.cloud` | Production, Preview |
| `VITE_CONVEX_SITE_URL` | `https://<deployment>.convex.site` | Production, Preview |

Optional (only if running Convex CLI tasks from Vercel):

| Variable | Value | Environment |
|----------|-------|-------------|
| `CONVEX_DEPLOYMENT` | `prod:<name>` | Production |

## How to get your Convex URL

1. Run `npx convex dev` locally
2. Or run `npx convex deploy` for production
3. Your deployment URL is shown in the Convex dashboard
